name: Happy Weekend~
description: You tends to get overwhelmed? Feeling sudden fatigue after facing the screen the whole hours? Well, we might thought that it will went away as the day pass, but here I present you, the ultimate fact of life. All of us are only reliving the same day over and over again, same misery day by day. So congratulations! You're not only feeling a bad day, you are living a bad life! Cheers!
